WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.950 align:middle line:90%
[SOMBER MUSIC]

00:00:02.950 --> 00:00:05.020 align:middle line:84%
>> I always dreamed
of becoming an artist,

00:00:05.020 --> 00:00:09.252 align:middle line:84%
but my parents said it wasn't
a practical career choice.

00:00:09.252 --> 00:00:11.880 align:middle line:84%
Despite their advice,
from a young age,

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:13.630 align:middle line:84%
I knew this was my
path and was determined

00:00:13.630 --> 00:00:16.848 align:middle line:84%
to do whatever it
took to get there.

00:00:16.848 --> 00:00:20.250 align:middle line:84%
After graduating high
school, I met Sarah.

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:22.124 align:middle line:84%
She was a couple of
years older than me

00:00:22.124 --> 00:00:24.624 align:middle line:84%
and had been supporting herself
by working as a video editor

00:00:24.624 --> 00:00:27.550 align:middle line:90%
in Los Angelese.

00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:30.130 align:middle line:84%
I was inspired by her
passion for making movies,

00:00:30.130 --> 00:00:31.990 align:middle line:84%
and we instantly
started collaborating

00:00:31.990 --> 00:00:35.580 align:middle line:90%
and became best friends.

00:00:35.580 --> 00:00:38.080 align:middle line:84%
In 2010, I won a
scholarship competition

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:39.940 align:middle line:84%
to go to art school
in San Francisco,

00:00:39.940 --> 00:00:43.080 align:middle line:90%
and we moved up there together.

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:45.730 align:middle line:84%
After living in this city
for a couple of years,

00:00:45.730 --> 00:00:48.860 align:middle line:84%
we are continuously inspired
by the melting pot of women

00:00:48.860 --> 00:00:51.750 align:middle line:90%
we met everywhere we went.

00:00:51.750 --> 00:00:53.260 align:middle line:84%
As we got to know
each of them, we

00:00:53.260 --> 00:00:55.960 align:middle line:84%
realized how similar our
fears and obstacles were

00:00:55.960 --> 00:01:00.630 align:middle line:84%
and how empowering it is to
hear other women's stories.

00:01:00.630 --> 00:01:03.782 align:middle line:84%
At school, I felt frustrated
by the media's representation

00:01:03.782 --> 00:01:06.240 align:middle line:84%
of women and felt like there
was little I could do about it

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:08.760 align:middle line:90%
by sitting in a classroom.

00:01:08.760 --> 00:01:10.470 align:middle line:84%
I decided to leave
school to make

00:01:10.470 --> 00:01:12.330 align:middle line:84%
art that empowers
women and girls

00:01:12.330 --> 00:01:15.490 align:middle line:90%
and focus on that full time.

00:01:15.490 --> 00:01:17.645 align:middle line:84%
It was a big deal for me
to give up my scholarship.

00:01:17.645 --> 00:01:20.748 align:middle line:84%
So I called Sarah, and
she met me for lunch.

00:01:20.748 --> 00:01:24.519 align:middle line:84%
We talked about all the
amazing women we knew,

00:01:24.519 --> 00:01:26.436 align:middle line:84%
and how many diverse
perspectives were missing

00:01:26.436 --> 00:01:28.793 align:middle line:90%
from movies and television.

00:01:28.793 --> 00:01:30.460 align:middle line:84%
We knew there had to
be other people who

00:01:30.460 --> 00:01:32.050 align:middle line:84%
wanted to hear
stories from women

00:01:32.050 --> 00:01:34.820 align:middle line:84%
of different ages,
backgrounds, and beliefs.

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.690 align:middle line:84%
So that day, we decided to
launch a crowdfunding campaign

00:01:37.690 --> 00:01:40.360 align:middle line:84%
to travel the United States
and make a documentary.

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:51.074 align:middle line:90%


00:01:51.074 --> 00:01:54.000 align:middle line:84%
>> It's really jumping
off of a cliff.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.310 align:middle line:84%
Like, you gotta jump off
the cliff and step right

00:01:56.310 --> 00:01:58.080 align:middle line:90%
into your fears.

00:01:58.080 --> 00:02:00.050 align:middle line:84%
And there's no--
there's no in between.

00:02:00.050 --> 00:02:04.440 align:middle line:90%


00:02:04.440 --> 00:02:06.170 align:middle line:90%
>> You take the risk.

00:02:06.170 --> 00:02:09.410 align:middle line:84%
And then the positive
things will come to you.

00:02:09.410 --> 00:02:13.588 align:middle line:84%
Everybody on this planet
should wish something.

00:02:13.588 --> 00:02:16.130 align:middle line:84%
>> I had to come to the point
where I'd be willing to give up

00:02:16.130 --> 00:02:17.590 align:middle line:90%
everything.

00:02:17.590 --> 00:02:19.810 align:middle line:84%
What I discovered is
that anything of value

00:02:19.810 --> 00:02:23.170 align:middle line:90%
doesn't really leave.

00:02:23.170 --> 00:02:27.360 align:middle line:84%
>> It may seem so big, or so
impossible, or so daunting,

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:29.580 align:middle line:90%
or so expensive, or so far.

00:02:29.580 --> 00:02:32.648 align:middle line:90%


00:02:32.648 --> 00:02:34.940 align:middle line:84%
>> Maybe you don't have a
car, and you don't have this,

00:02:34.940 --> 00:02:35.898 align:middle line:90%
or you don't have that.

00:02:35.898 --> 00:02:39.090 align:middle line:84%
Like, there are always
ways to get what you want.

00:02:39.090 --> 00:02:41.946 align:middle line:90%


00:02:41.946 --> 00:02:44.670 align:middle line:84%
>> When you open your heart
and you believe in yourself,

00:02:44.670 --> 00:02:45.870 align:middle line:90%
you're willing to mess up.

00:02:45.870 --> 00:02:48.500 align:middle line:90%
You're willing to jump full out.

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:50.320 align:middle line:84%
And that's when
the magic happens.

00:02:50.320 --> 00:02:53.430 align:middle line:90%


00:02:53.430 --> 00:02:55.980 align:middle line:84%
>> If you just trust and
begin, things unfold.

00:02:55.980 --> 00:02:57.432 align:middle line:90%
People show up.

00:02:57.432 --> 00:03:00.336 align:middle line:90%


00:03:00.336 --> 00:03:03.240 align:middle line:84%
It's like they drop
right out of the sky,

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:04.692 align:middle line:90%
right when you need them.

00:03:04.692 --> 00:03:10.990 align:middle line:90%


00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:13.570 align:middle line:84%
>> As soon as we decided
to take this leap of faith,

00:03:13.570 --> 00:03:16.510 align:middle line:84%
magical things started
happening everywhere we went.

00:03:16.510 --> 00:03:21.010 align:middle line:84%
Just days after reaching our
Kickstarter goal, we met Chirp.

00:03:21.010 --> 00:03:23.530 align:middle line:84%
>> Chirp is this incredible guy
who had just traveled across

00:03:23.530 --> 00:03:25.810 align:middle line:84%
the country in his school
bus that he converted to run

00:03:25.810 --> 00:03:27.775 align:middle line:90%
on vegetable oil.

00:03:27.775 --> 00:03:29.650 align:middle line:84%
Within minutes of meeting
him and telling him

00:03:29.650 --> 00:03:32.890 align:middle line:84%
about our project, he said, let
me think about it overnight,

00:03:32.890 --> 00:03:36.250 align:middle line:84%
but I'm pretty sure I
want you to take my bus.

00:03:36.250 --> 00:03:37.820 align:middle line:90%
>> We were totally blown away.

00:03:37.820 --> 00:03:39.820 align:middle line:84%
We couldn't believe that
someone we had just met

00:03:39.820 --> 00:03:43.373 align:middle line:84%
was willing to give us
such a generous gift.

00:03:43.373 --> 00:03:45.790 align:middle line:84%
>> The next day, Chirp called
to tell us that he wanted us

00:03:45.790 --> 00:03:48.610 align:middle line:84%
to take his beloved home on
wheels for our cross-country

00:03:48.610 --> 00:03:49.420 align:middle line:90%
adventure.

00:03:49.420 --> 00:03:51.790 align:middle line:84%
And his magical school
bus became the catalyst

00:03:51.790 --> 00:03:53.030 align:middle line:90%
for everything else to come.

00:03:53.030 --> 00:03:56.432 align:middle line:90%
[PIANO MUSIC]

00:03:56.432 --> 00:03:58.870 align:middle line:90%


00:03:58.870 --> 00:04:02.080 align:middle line:84%
>> When I got your email,
of course, automatically,

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:03.670 align:middle line:90%
being who I am, I got nervous.

00:04:03.670 --> 00:04:04.720 align:middle line:90%
I'm like, oh, my god.

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:06.230 align:middle line:90%
They want me to paint a bus.

00:04:06.230 --> 00:04:09.490 align:middle line:84%
There was something inside
me told me, like, Michelle,

00:04:09.490 --> 00:04:12.190 align:middle line:90%
put all your fears aside.

00:04:12.190 --> 00:04:13.190 align:middle line:90%
I have to do this.

00:04:13.190 --> 00:04:17.740 align:middle line:90%


00:04:17.740 --> 00:04:21.779 align:middle line:84%
I'm hoping that when you're
riding through the country,

00:04:21.779 --> 00:04:24.000 align:middle line:84%
everyone who sees it will
just be touched by it.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:27.153 align:middle line:84%
They won't even have to know
what's going on with the bus.

00:04:27.153 --> 00:04:29.820 align:middle line:84%
They don't even have to know why
there's all these women painted

00:04:29.820 --> 00:04:30.620 align:middle line:90%
on the bus.

00:04:30.620 --> 00:04:33.460 align:middle line:84%
But just as long
as they're touched,

00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:35.550 align:middle line:84%
and maybe they just want
to better themselves

00:04:35.550 --> 00:04:37.570 align:middle line:84%
just because you just
drove down their block.

00:04:37.570 --> 00:04:38.370 align:middle line:90%
You know?

00:04:38.370 --> 00:04:42.420 align:middle line:84%
Like, wow, that could be
their changing moment in life.

00:04:42.420 --> 00:04:45.240 align:middle line:84%
You guys are just going to
leave a beautiful trail.

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:47.433 align:middle line:84%
And then maybe people will
just want to follow it.

00:04:47.433 --> 00:04:50.391 align:middle line:90%
[PEACEFUL MUSIC]

00:04:50.391 --> 00:05:10.610 align:middle line:90%


00:05:10.610 --> 00:05:12.270 align:middle line:84%
>> Two days ago,
I didn't know you.

00:05:12.270 --> 00:05:13.160 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:14.510 align:middle line:90%
And you didn't know me.

00:05:14.510 --> 00:05:18.470 align:middle line:84%
And that's the cool part,
I think, about just plain

00:05:18.470 --> 00:05:24.420 align:middle line:84%
being in the moment and living
is that things find you.

00:05:24.420 --> 00:05:29.910 align:middle line:84%
>> So I contacted you because
I saw your bus outside

00:05:29.910 --> 00:05:32.250 align:middle line:90%
of my work, well, my ex-work.

00:05:32.250 --> 00:05:34.980 align:middle line:90%
But I had just quit.

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:37.380 align:middle line:84%
And immediately when I walked
out and I saw your bus,

00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:41.430 align:middle line:84%
I thought to myself, this is one
of those cosmic moments where

00:05:41.430 --> 00:05:44.520 align:middle line:84%
timing is aligning and
something weird is happening.

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:46.695 align:middle line:84%
And I thought to
myself, I can do that.

00:05:46.695 --> 00:05:48.270 align:middle line:90%
Like, there's a bus right there.

00:05:48.270 --> 00:05:51.060 align:middle line:84%
And that's like, just right
in my face, telling me, like,

00:05:51.060 --> 00:05:52.510 align:middle line:90%
yes, this is the right choice.

00:05:52.510 --> 00:05:54.240 align:middle line:90%
This was the right decision.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.160 align:middle line:84%
You should be going
and doing what

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:57.960 align:middle line:84%
you want to do
and not be wasting

00:05:57.960 --> 00:06:00.750 align:middle line:84%
your time in a place
that doesn't really

00:06:00.750 --> 00:06:06.064 align:middle line:84%
allow you to make any sort of
meaningful mark with your life.

00:06:06.064 --> 00:06:08.670 align:middle line:84%
I think there's, like,
a sense of strength

00:06:08.670 --> 00:06:12.420 align:middle line:84%
behind being able to express
exactly how you're feeling

00:06:12.420 --> 00:06:14.670 align:middle line:90%
and being real about it.

00:06:14.670 --> 00:06:17.350 align:middle line:84%
>> I think it's a human need,
to be seen for who you are,

00:06:17.350 --> 00:06:18.150 align:middle line:90%
who you truly are.

00:06:18.150 --> 00:06:20.590 align:middle line:84%
I mean, that's what
we want, right?

00:06:20.590 --> 00:06:24.550 align:middle line:84%
>> When I saw your project, I
saw that that was exactly what

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:26.080 align:middle line:90%
you were doing.

00:06:26.080 --> 00:06:27.190 align:middle line:90%
There's no dogma.

00:06:27.190 --> 00:06:28.360 align:middle line:90%
There's no rules.

00:06:28.360 --> 00:06:30.140 align:middle line:90%
There's no shoulds.

00:06:30.140 --> 00:06:34.000 align:middle line:84%
It's seeing people and
what they have to offer.

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:38.290 align:middle line:84%
>> Each being is a different
expression of this life.

00:06:38.290 --> 00:06:42.220 align:middle line:84%
And everyone is doing it so
differently, so distinctly.

00:06:42.220 --> 00:06:44.710 align:middle line:84%
>> I've fallen in love with
so many amazing people when

00:06:44.710 --> 00:06:48.010 align:middle line:84%
I've traveled, just people that
I just would have never met had

00:06:48.010 --> 00:06:51.760 align:middle line:84%
I just not been granted the
big gift of leaving my place

00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:54.260 align:middle line:90%
of knowingness.

00:06:54.260 --> 00:06:55.680 align:middle line:84%
>> Jeez, if I had
to do it again,

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:57.160 align:middle line:90%
I'd do all the same things.

00:06:57.160 --> 00:06:59.710 align:middle line:90%
I had way too much fun.

00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:02.620 align:middle line:84%
I was a flight attendant
with Flying Tigers, which

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:04.150 align:middle line:90%
is a non-scheduled airline.

00:07:04.150 --> 00:07:07.980 align:middle line:84%
We flew anywhere in
the world at any time.

00:07:07.980 --> 00:07:10.330 align:middle line:84%
And once, I was on this
flight with zebras.

00:07:10.330 --> 00:07:12.730 align:middle line:84%
They were going from one
zoo to the other zoo.

00:07:12.730 --> 00:07:15.195 align:middle line:84%
And I had my luggage
too close to the zebras.

00:07:15.195 --> 00:07:16.570 align:middle line:84%
And it went potty
on my suitcase.

00:07:16.570 --> 00:07:18.690 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:07:18.690 --> 00:07:22.530 align:middle line:84%
The only thing I haven't done
that I really wanted to do

00:07:22.530 --> 00:07:23.610 align:middle line:90%
is hop a freighter.

00:07:23.610 --> 00:07:26.412 align:middle line:90%
[TRAIN HORN]

00:07:26.412 --> 00:07:28.750 align:middle line:90%


00:07:28.750 --> 00:07:32.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Sometimes my heart aches to
go back to that really magical

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:33.940 align:middle line:90%
time in my life.

00:07:33.940 --> 00:07:38.470 align:middle line:84%
It was four ladies and, you
know, a dog, and a banjo.

00:07:38.470 --> 00:07:43.000 align:middle line:84%
And it was definitely the
most empowering experience

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:47.050 align:middle line:84%
I've had in my life, just
being this tiny, precious,

00:07:47.050 --> 00:07:51.760 align:middle line:84%
clandestine cargo on
this giant machine that

00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:54.400 align:middle line:90%
is moving to somewhere.

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:57.040 align:middle line:84%
A destination that you
don't necessarily know

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:59.590 align:middle line:84%
is one of the most
amazing feelings

00:07:59.590 --> 00:08:02.530 align:middle line:90%
that you could ever have.

00:08:02.530 --> 00:08:03.910 align:middle line:90%
>> I didn't do that.

00:08:03.910 --> 00:08:06.183 align:middle line:84%
But I did hitchhike
from New York to here.

00:08:06.183 --> 00:08:07.600 align:middle line:84%
It only took us
three days, and we

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:11.050 align:middle line:84%
got dropped off right
at our front door.

00:08:11.050 --> 00:08:12.490 align:middle line:90%
That was cool.

00:08:12.490 --> 00:08:14.770 align:middle line:84%
>> It's unusual, I
would say, for people,

00:08:14.770 --> 00:08:22.210 align:middle line:84%
and somewhat alarming, to look
at women trusting the world.

00:08:22.210 --> 00:08:23.770 align:middle line:84%
People would be
like, oh, my god.

00:08:23.770 --> 00:08:25.677 align:middle line:84%
What are you ladies
doing on here?

00:08:25.677 --> 00:08:27.385 align:middle line:84%
Like, how are you
fending for yourselves?

00:08:27.385 --> 00:08:29.285 align:middle line:90%
>> You traveled alone?

00:08:29.285 --> 00:08:30.085 align:middle line:90%
But how?

00:08:30.085 --> 00:08:31.390 align:middle line:90%
Weren't you bored?

00:08:31.390 --> 00:08:32.630 align:middle line:90%
Weren't you scared?

00:08:32.630 --> 00:08:33.520 align:middle line:90%
Weren't you lonely?

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:36.070 align:middle line:90%
And it's like, oh, my god, no.

00:08:36.070 --> 00:08:39.169 align:middle line:84%
You guys make it seem like I
took a rocket ship to Mars.

00:08:39.169 --> 00:08:41.147 align:middle line:84%
Like, this is really
not that scary.

00:08:41.147 --> 00:08:43.480 align:middle line:84%
>> It's an interesting being
traveling around the world.

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:45.670 align:middle line:84%
You know, you have to trust
yourself, your instinct.

00:08:45.670 --> 00:08:48.190 align:middle line:84%
You have to trust your
intuition, your own center.

00:08:48.190 --> 00:08:49.720 align:middle line:84%
And you have to
trust other people.

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:51.430 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:08:51.430 --> 00:08:54.010 align:middle line:84%
And so there's an exchange
that could put you

00:08:54.010 --> 00:08:56.300 align:middle line:90%
in a vulnerable position.

00:08:56.300 --> 00:08:58.640 align:middle line:84%
>> No matter where we went,
whether it was a big city

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:00.260 align:middle line:84%
or a small suburban
neighborhood,

00:09:00.260 --> 00:09:01.880 align:middle line:84%
there always seemed
to be somebody,

00:09:01.880 --> 00:09:05.000 align:middle line:84%
somewhere who felt compelled
to tell us to be careful out

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:07.800 align:middle line:90%
there.

00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:09.330 align:middle line:90%
>> We traveled 10,000 miles.

00:09:09.330 --> 00:09:12.390 align:middle line:84%
And we spent almost 200 nights
sleeping in parking lots,

00:09:12.390 --> 00:09:15.140 align:middle line:84%
along mountain tops,
and on city streets.

00:09:15.140 --> 00:09:17.310 align:middle line:84%
But in the end, the
most notable encounters

00:09:17.310 --> 00:09:19.890 align:middle line:84%
were love notes left on our
windshield and invitations

00:09:19.890 --> 00:09:22.140 align:middle line:90%
for home-cooked meals.

00:09:22.140 --> 00:09:24.283 align:middle line:84%
>> We learned that people
are inherently good.

00:09:24.283 --> 00:09:26.700 align:middle line:84%
And when you're striving to
make the world a better place,

00:09:26.700 --> 00:09:31.230 align:middle line:84%
someone will always show up to
help you out in a time of need.

00:09:31.230 --> 00:09:35.970 align:middle line:84%
>> When one of us activate that
knowingness within ourselves

00:09:35.970 --> 00:09:39.480 align:middle line:84%
and we follow the path, that
impulse from our hearts,

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:42.720 align:middle line:84%
it is irresistible to
other people around us.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:46.560 align:middle line:84%
And it gives them permission
to also take the leap.

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:50.850 align:middle line:84%
And those who maybe have
an extra bed in their house

00:09:50.850 --> 00:09:54.350 align:middle line:84%
or have a few extra
dollars to spare

00:09:54.350 --> 00:09:58.360 align:middle line:84%
are so touched by
that activation

00:09:58.360 --> 00:10:03.310 align:middle line:84%
that they yearn to support
us because they're also

00:10:03.310 --> 00:10:05.230 align:middle line:84%
being gifted with
this permission

00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:07.240 align:middle line:84%
to support themselves
in their path

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:08.860 align:middle line:90%
when they're in our presence.

00:10:08.860 --> 00:10:12.610 align:middle line:84%
>> There's a traditional Navajo
prayer that's "as we walk,

00:10:12.610 --> 00:10:13.900 align:middle line:90%
beauty is on every side.

00:10:13.900 --> 00:10:14.800 align:middle line:90%
Beauty is before.

