00:14:00.420 --> 00:14:02.500 align:middle line:90%
>> My name is Noramay Cadena.

00:14:02.500 --> 00:14:05.170 align:middle line:84%
My family is an immigrant
family from Mexico.

00:14:05.170 --> 00:14:08.580 align:middle line:84%
And before me, no one
had ever been to college.

00:14:08.580 --> 00:14:11.700 align:middle line:84%
When I was growing up, we lived
in the house my parents rented.

00:14:11.700 --> 00:14:13.020 align:middle line:90%
It had two bedrooms.

00:14:13.020 --> 00:14:15.900 align:middle line:84%
And at one time, there were
10 people living in it.

00:14:15.900 --> 00:14:19.800 align:middle line:90%
I remember living without water.

00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:22.440 align:middle line:84%
I remember going without
electricity at times.

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:25.898 align:middle line:84%
So as I was growing up,
my mom said repeatedly,

00:14:25.898 --> 00:14:26.940 align:middle line:90%
