00:14:26.940 --> 00:14:29.880 align:middle line:84%
You have to do well
so you're not like me.

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:31.680 align:middle line:84%
I don't want you
to have this life.

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:34.590 align:middle line:84%
