her for a summer.

00:14:39.130 --> 00:14:42.930 align:middle line:84%
So for a whole summer, I got
to sit for eight hours a day

00:14:42.930 --> 00:14:47.520 align:middle line:84%
and put hooks on the
end of bungee cords.

00:14:47.520 --> 00:14:49.930 align:middle line:84%
And it was a horrible
experience, and I hated it.

00:14:49.930 --> 00:14:54.420 align:middle line:84%
I mean, things like that
are very hard to forget.

00:14:54.420 --> 00:14:58.080 align:middle line:84%
And there were the little
pieces along the way that really

00:14:58.080 --> 00:15:02.400 align:middle line:84%
fueled a desire in me to give
my parents a different life

00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:04.590 align:middle line:84%
and to enable that
opportunity for other people

00:15:04.590 --> 00:15:06.640 align:middle line:90%
around my community.

00:15:06.640 --> 00:15:10.530 align:middle line:84%
It took me a while to forgive
myself for putting myself

00:15:10.530 --> 00:15:12.000 align:middle line:90%
in that situation.

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:14.820 align:middle line:84%
As a teen mom, I really
felt like my parents

00:15:14.820 --> 00:15:19.090 align:middle line:84%
had put so much faith in me,
had sacrificed so much for me.

00:15:19.090 --> 00:15:22.020 align:middle line:84%
And I felt like I was
letting them down.

00:15:22.020 --> 00:15:24.520 align:middle line:84%
There was a gentleman who had
graduated from my high school,

00:15:24.520 --> 00:15:26.180 align:middle line:90%
and he was an MIT student.

00:15:26.180 --> 00:15:27.270 align:middle line:90%
And I go to meet with him.

00:15:27.270 --> 00:15:29.655 align:middle line:84%
And he says, you know, I
hear you're good at math

00:15:29.655 --> 00:15:30.780 align:middle line:90%
and you're good at science.

00:15:30.780 --> 00:15:32.940 align:middle line:84%
Have you ever
considered engineering?

00:15:32.940 --> 00:15:34.700 align:middle line:90%
And I said, what's that?

00:15:34.700 --> 00:15:36.810 align:middle line:84%
At the time when
I had my daughter,

00:15:36.810 --> 00:15:39.350 align:middle line:84%
