00:15:40.850 --> 00:15:42.960 align:middle line:90%
Are you friggin' crazy.?

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:45.106 align:middle line:84%
Finally, I said,
look, I'll apply.

00:15:45.106 --> 00:15:47.720 align:middle line:90%
And I got admitted.

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:51.530 align:middle line:84%
My daughter was a little
over one when we packed up

00:15:51.530 --> 00:15:53.890 align:middle line:90%
