being a bad mother.

00:15:57.320 --> 00:15:59.320 align:middle line:90%
You need to focus on parenting.

00:15:59.320 --> 00:16:02.000 align:middle line:84%
But I was trying so
hard to be two people,

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:04.730 align:middle line:84%
