00:16:09.650 --> 00:16:13.340 align:middle line:84%
It was a big goal
of a better life.

00:16:13.340 --> 00:16:16.150 align:middle line:84%
When you're successful,
it doesn't only help you.

00:16:16.150 --> 00:16:17.930 align:middle line:90%
It helps your siblings.

00:16:17.930 --> 00:16:19.180 align:middle line:90%
It helps your parents.

00:16:19.180 --> 00:16:20.680 align:middle line:90%
It helps your children.

00:16:20.680 --> 00:16:23.030 align:middle line:84%
And it's an
eye-opening experience

00:16:23.030 --> 00:16:25.120 align:middle line:84%
for so many people
