00:51:57.620 --> 00:52:00.490 align:middle line:90%
and through philanthropy.

00:52:00.490 --> 00:52:03.700 align:middle line:84%
>> Our generation coming into
the workforce was really about

00:52:03.700 --> 00:52:06.880 align:middle line:84%
how to be like a man, if
