00:52:08.110 --> 00:52:09.220 align:middle line:90%
I really did.

00:52:09.220 --> 00:52:10.500 align:middle line:90%
They were more comfortable.

00:52:10.500 --> 00:52:13.180 align:middle line:84%
But the saying was, was
