00:55:15.340 --> 00:55:16.140 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm Muslim--

00:55:16.140 --> 00:55:18.330 align:middle line:84%
Muslim, as you can
see, and believe

00:55:18.330 --> 00:55:21.060 align:middle line:84%
that women should be respected
for their intelligence

00:55:21.060 --> 00:55:23.400 align:middle line:84%
and their skills, not
for their body image.

00:55:23.400 --> 00:55:25.230 align:middle line:84%
And so people put
me in this category

00:55:25.230 --> 00:55:27.960 align:middle line:84%
