empowering women.

00:57:28.940 --> 00:57:31.190 align:middle line:84%
>> (ON TV) Know your
role, and shut your mouth.

00:57:31.190 --> 00:57:34.850 align:middle line:84%
>> (ON TV) Women have become
the breadwinners in this country

00:57:34.850 --> 00:57:37.940 align:middle line:84%
