00:57:42.670 --> 00:57:43.740 align:middle line:90%
They're less ambitious.

00:57:43.740 --> 00:57:45.020 align:middle line:90%
They don't go the extra mile.

00:57:45.020 --> 00:57:45.860 align:middle line:84%
>> (ON TV) Why am
I sitting here?

00:57:45.860 --> 00:57:46.300 align:middle line:84%
>> (ON TV) They don't
work all weekend.

00:57:46.300 --> 00:57:46.810 align:middle line:90%
>> (ON TV) I'm sitting here.

00:57:46.810 --> 00:57:47.780 align:middle line:84%
>> (ON TV) You're
making a mistake.

00:57:47.780 --> 00:57:50.710 align:middle line:84%
