home with a husband and chores.

00:57:50.710 --> 00:57:51.770 align:middle line:90%
>> (ON TV) Oh boy.

00:57:51.770 --> 00:57:54.410 align:middle line:84%
>> Those forces that want
to diminish a certain group

00:57:54.410 --> 00:57:57.590 align:middle line:84%
of people are out there, so we
have to be out there as well,

00:57:57.590 --> 00:58:00.860 align:middle line:84%
you know, always providing
that push and pull and that

00:58:00.860 --> 00:58:04.020 align:middle line:90%
environment of many ideas.

00:58:04.020 --> 00:58:06.800 align:middle line:84%
>> I remember coming home
from college after I had taken

00:58:06.800 --> 00:58:10.550 align:middle line:84%
my first class that taught
what feminist theory was,

00:58:10.550 --> 00:58:12.690 align:middle line:84%
and I asked my mom,
like, are you a feminist?

00:58:12.690 --> 00:58:15.230 align:middle line:84%
And she immediately was
like, no, that's man-hating.

00:58:15.230 --> 00:58:18.980 align:middle line:84%
And she had a completely
different opinions

00:58:18.980 --> 00:58:21.560 align:middle line:84%
to what my sociology
professor was telling me.

00:58:21.560 --> 00:58:24.110 align:middle line:84%
>> A lot of times, folks will
think of feminism as a dirty

00:58:24.110 --> 00:58:26.100 align:middle line:90%
word, and it's not at all.

00:58:26.100 --> 00:58:28.970 align:middle line:84%
It just means that a
woman is equal to a man.

00:58:28.970 --> 00:58:32.040 align:middle line:90%
[SOLEMN MUSIC]

00:58:32.040 --> 00:58:32.840 align:middle line:90%


00:58:32.840 --> 00:58:35.430 align:middle line:84%
>> I think the ultimate
goal of feminism,

00:58:35.430 --> 00:58:38.220 align:middle line:84%
