00:58:44.220 --> 00:58:48.390 align:middle line:84%
that half the population not
being empowered for the greater

00:58:48.390 --> 00:58:51.120 align:middle line:84%
history of humanity
is a huge problem.

00:58:51.120 --> 00:58:52.620 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's
the kind of issue

00:58:52.620 --> 00:58:54.312 align:middle line:84%
that you're taking
up with your project.

00:58:54.312 --> 00:58:55.770 align:middle line:84%
And maybe, in a
way, that will help

00:58:55.770 --> 00:58:57.990 align:middle line:84%
people relate to
what feminism could

00:58:57.990 --> 00:58:59.990 align:middle line:84%
be-- maybe not always
what it has been,

00:58:59.990 --> 00:59:01.470 align:middle line:90%
but where it could go.

00:59:01.470 --> 00:59:04.740 align:middle line:84%
>> It's so important for
women to find your strength

00:59:04.740 --> 00:59:09.780 align:middle line:84%
and your power internally and
gather together because we have

00:59:09.780 --> 00:59:13.253 align:middle line:84%
a lot of work to do
in saving our mother.

00:59:13.253 --> 00:59:16.500 align:middle line:84%
You know, we went on this
course of industrialization

00:59:16.500 --> 00:59:20.940 align:middle line:84%
and became drawn to individual
personal gain, and material

00:59:20.940 --> 00:59:23.880 align:middle line:84%
