those things that

00:59:23.880 --> 00:59:26.582 align:middle line:84%
are not going to
bring us joy, or love,

00:59:26.582 --> 00:59:30.820 align:middle line:90%
or save us from destruction.

00:59:30.820 --> 00:59:36.530 align:middle line:84%
It's like we stepped outside
the circle of life, really.

00:59:36.530 --> 00:59:38.750 align:middle line:90%
>> It's not my goals.

00:59:38.750 --> 00:59:41.615 align:middle line:90%
It's the goal for everybody.

00:59:41.615 --> 00:59:44.380 align:middle line:84%
We want everybody to have
jobs and have a participation

00:59:44.380 --> 00:59:46.782 align:middle line:84%
