within our community.

00:59:46.782 --> 00:59:49.720 align:middle line:90%
And I know that I can cook.

00:59:49.720 --> 00:59:55.550 align:middle line:84%
So even though I want to
be a pop star secretly,

00:59:55.550 --> 00:59:58.388 align:middle line:84%
I'm totally happy cutting
carrots, and I'm having a ball.

00:59:58.388 --> 01:00:00.430 align:middle line:84%
And I get to sing in the
kitchen, so that's cool.

01:00:00.430 --> 01:00:02.780 align:middle line:84%
And that's a way that I
can constantly participate

01:00:02.780 --> 01:00:05.540 align:middle line:90%
in the world in a positive way.

01:00:05.540 --> 01:00:09.890 align:middle line:84%
>> Everyone has something
unique or beautiful about them,

01:00:09.890 --> 01:00:13.305 align:middle line:84%
including me, including you,
including just a homeless

01:00:13.305 --> 01:00:14.180 align:middle line:90%
person on the street.

01:00:14.180 --> 01:00:17.180 align:middle line:90%
Everyone has something to add.

01:00:17.180 --> 01:00:20.120 align:middle line:84%
>> We all have the
spark of life within us,

01:00:20.120 --> 01:00:22.670 align:middle line:84%
whether you call it God,
Goddess, the Divine,

01:00:22.670 --> 01:00:25.100 align:middle line:84%
