likeness of this great source

01:00:28.420 --> 01:00:29.220 align:middle line:90%
energy.

01:00:29.220 --> 01:00:31.262 align:middle line:84%
>> There's all these
different type of religions,

01:00:31.262 --> 01:00:33.577 align:middle line:84%
and they swear they
have different gods,

01:00:33.577 --> 01:00:35.410 align:middle line:84%
but I don't necessarily
think it's that way.

01:00:35.410 --> 01:00:36.870 align:middle line:90%
I think that it's the same god.

01:00:36.870 --> 01:00:39.900 align:middle line:84%
They're just practicing
it differently.

01:00:39.900 --> 01:00:41.300 align:middle line:90%
They all talk to the same god.

01:00:41.300 --> 01:00:43.140 align:middle line:84%
It's just their
interpretation of that god.

01:00:43.140 --> 01:00:47.630 align:middle line:84%
>> It's a separation theology
