01:00:47.630 --> 01:00:50.330 align:middle line:84%
When we feel we are separate--
separate from God, like God's

01:00:50.330 --> 01:00:52.980 align:middle line:84%
out there, that sets up
that kind of judgment.

01:00:52.980 --> 01:00:56.360 align:middle line:84%
But if you shift that
to oneness theology,

01:00:56.360 --> 01:00:58.340 align:middle line:90%
that means that you're God.

01:00:58.340 --> 01:00:59.140 align:middle line:90%
