01:22:55.496 --> 01:22:58.415 align:middle line:90%
[PIANO MUSIC]

01:22:58.415 --> 01:22:59.740 align:middle line:90%


01:22:59.740 --> 01:23:02.410 align:middle line:84%
>> What is the
