01:24:39.030 --> 01:24:39.960 align:middle line:90%
for that person.

01:24:39.960 --> 01:24:45.810 align:middle line:84%
>> We can be forces of
understanding that life is

01:24:45.810 --> 01:24:50.540 align:middle line:84%
complicated, and it's painful,
